Rhinox stopped short from running as he stopped firing. "Just don't 
hurt him."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
BH look around. He entered the engine room. He put some bombs down
and 
walked out.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
BlastRage fired the skimmers 10x Gernade launcher at Rhinox. He fired 
some optics at HotRod.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~`
Rhinox flies in the air 10 feet as the gernades Hit down infront of 
him. He hits a tree, the tree splits apart. He poped up and fires at 
BlastRage.
